data.description: This 4/3+ office and formal dining room is spacious and ready to impress! Head inside and you will immediately take note of the large living area with stunning electric fireplace with wooden mantle.  Upon entering, to the left is the office which dispays a custom barn door and to the right, the formal dining room.  The kitchen offers granite countertops, a breakfast nook, stainless steel appliances, abundant cabinet space, and a pantry. . The oversized master bedroom features an en suite bathroom with a tiled shower, soaking tub, double vanities, a walk in closet and linen closet!  This home has a split floorplan with additional bedrooms on the opposite side of home. Head out back to the fully fenced back yard with a covered and screened in porch! Schedule your showing today!
